=== Von Mises ===

==== (% class=&amp;#34;StyleStyleBold12pt&amp;#34; style=&amp;#34;font-weight:normal&amp;#34; %)NEG interp is useless hair-splitting. “restriction” is intended to make production more difficult and eliminate particular means of production(%%) ====

(% class=&amp;#34;MsoNormal&amp;#34; style=&amp;#34;margin-left:.25in&amp;#34; %)
