==== This failure to understand the true scope of Anti-Blackness in the Status Quo is exemplified within Resolutional policies ~-~- mistakenly searching for ways to Federally incentivize “Green Jobs, Not Jails” ignores the Federal Restrictions which are __already__ creating Green Jobs __IN__ Jails. ====

